## src/ layout (WinCanister)

```text
src/
├── main.mo
├── migrations/
├── api/v1/          # LotteryController, RoundController, WinnerController, HealthController
├── services/        # LotteryService, RoundService, DepositService, WinnerService, …
├── repositories/
├── storage/
├── models/
├── dto/
├── validators/
├── config/
├── ledger/          # LedgerClient, IcpIndexClient
├── randomness/
├── utils/
└── testing/         # TestHarness (used by backend/testing locally)
```

## Layer rule

```text
Controller → Service → Repository → Storage
```

Controllers stay thin. Business logic lives in services. Stable memory only in storage.

## Quick commands

```bash
bash scripts/run-tests.sh
DFX_NETWORK=ic bash scripts/build-lottery.sh
bash scripts/verify-mainnet.sh
```

See [motok/deploy-guide/release-checklist.md](./motok/deploy-guide/release-checklist.md) before every mainnet deploy.
